PrettyB boxplot.default function

Source: R/boxplot.R
boxplot.prettyB.Rd

This function overrides the default arguments. See ?graphics::boxplot.default

# S3 method for prettyB
boxplot(
  x,
  ...,
  range = 1.5,
  width = NULL,
  varwidth = FALSE,
  notch = FALSE,
  outline = TRUE,
  names,
  plot = TRUE,
  border = par("fg"),
  col = NULL,
  log = "",
  pars = list(boxwex = 0.8, staplewex = 0.5, outwex = 0.5),
  horizontal = FALSE,
  add = FALSE,
  at = NULL
)

  at = NULL
)
